  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3467390/extras/ca2974ce759941a095febf5c723007df.poster.avif?t=1767103178\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3467390/extras/ca2974ce759941a095febf5c723007df.webm?t=1767103178\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3467390/extras/ca2974ce759941a095febf5c723007df.mp4?t=1767103178\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3467390/extras/a829943e637c875be178f168871b1011.webp?t=1767103178\" width=616 height=50 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blink</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make a sound</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trust your friends</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run out of batteries</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3467390/extras/a6b1b5f3b83ff57c09d5943e9df99d06.poster.avif?t=1767103178\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3467390/extras/a6b1b5f3b83ff57c09d5943e9df99d06.webm?t=1767103178\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3467390/extras/a6b1b5f3b83ff57c09d5943e9df99d06.mp4?t=1767103178\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3467390/extras/c478bf94208942060be0eb35248da09d.webp?t=1767103178\" width=616 height=50 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The codes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Real smart</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To the safe room</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3467390/extras/6bf9b0b759bb58e73bb2cdb2d12733f3.poster.avif?t=1767103178\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3467390/extras/6bf9b0b759bb58e73bb2cdb2d12733f3.webm?t=1767103178\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3467390/extras/6bf9b0b759bb58e73bb2cdb2d12733f3.mp4?t=1767103178\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3467390/extras/8d4542593c66a68a8fd3e29d956fd00c.webp?t=1767103178\" width=616 height=50 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trouble</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tricks up your sleeve</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3467390/extras/1fe7762305777a5edf09a00278f36152.poster.avif?t=1767103178\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3467390/extras/1fe7762305777a5edf09a00278f36152.webm?t=1767103178\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3467390/extras/1fe7762305777a5edf09a00278f36152.mp4?t=1767103178\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3467390/extras/a3031ee3170b463263c4150c229ee80e.webp?t=1767103178\" width=616 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>DON’T GET GOT is a multiplayer co-op horror game of deception. You’re locked inside and something is out to get you. Find the key. Use the environment and collaborate with other players until they no longer serve your needs.</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Co-op multiplayer with up to 8 players</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A large school with randomised objectives and safe rooms</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Easy to learn, hard to master social deception gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Intelligent creatures out to get you</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tools to solve problems: scanner, flashlight and decoys</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Proximity chat   </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3467390/extras/b3ab309fb0cd9a123f21677f1deeb676.avif?t=1767103178\" width=616 height=256 /></span></p>",
